the Classical Music Club.

4
00:01:40,083 --> 00:01:43,291
Huh? What made you decide
to quit all of a sudden?

5
00:01:43,375 --> 00:01:46,083
I think you have a natural
talent for the piano- it'd be

6
00:01:46,166 --> 00:01:49,125
a shame to waste it. So forget
about quitting and come back

7
00:01:49,208 --> 00:01:50,625
to the club.

8
00:01:50,708 --> 00:01:53,083
