you're sure to be popular

9
00:01:53,166 --> 00:01:54,750
with all the ladies.

10
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:58,041
But that's gonna take too long!

11
00:01:58,125 --> 00:02:00,375
I don't have that much time!

12
00:02:10,416 --> 00:02:14,333
The top floor
of the south building,

13
00:02:14,416 --> 00:02:17,291
at the end
of the north hallway.

14
00:02:22,291 --> 00:02:25,000
In a music room
that's never used.

15
00:02:26,583 --> 00:02:29,916
This is it. This is the place.

16
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:47,166
Welcome to the Ouran Host Club.

17
00:02:47,250 --> 00:02:48,333
