just called me, little boy?

25
00:03:11,583 --> 00:03:12,916
The "King"?

26
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:17,166
The "King"! Yes, I'm the king
of the Ouran host club!

27
00:03:17,250 --> 00:03:19,916
Long live the host king!

28
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:23,666
I'm an elementary
5th year, Shiro Takaoji!

29
00:03:26,500 --> 00:03:29,958
I want the Host Club King to
take me on as an apprentice!

30
00:03:36,166 --> 00:03:39,791
The Grade-School Host
is the Naughty Type!

31
00:03:39,875 --> 00:03:42,958
Oh my, Tamaki,
you have an apprentice?

32
00:03:43,041 --> 00:03:44,458
Yes. He's still
in elementary school,

33
00:03:44,541 --> 00:03:47,541
but I like
the fire in his eyes.

34
00:03:47,625 --> 00:03:49,541
But are you sure it's okay
for such a young boy

35
