There is a theory
that people are considered

44
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:13,291
more beautiful the closer they
are viewed. Tamaki seems to

45
00:04:13,375 --> 00:04:18,125
live by that theory.
Well, let's leave them alone.

46
00:04:18,208 --> 00:04:19,875
You naughty girl,
you've drawn me

47
00:04:19,958 --> 00:04:23,125
to the forbidden fruit, dearest.
You're a mermaid who's

48
00:04:23,208 --> 00:04:27,750
brought light into my lonely
sea. My mermaid princess.

49
00:04:27,833 --> 00:04:29,833
I remind you of a mermaid?

50
00:04:29,916 --> 00:04:32,250
You look more like the carp
that swim in my pond at home.

51
00:04:32,333 --> 00:04:34,333
