you know how kids are-
they can't help but be honest.

55
00:04:40,875 --> 00:04:42,916
Honest?

56
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,458
But that's just his opinion!
I wouldn't say that

57
00:04:44,541 --> 00:04:46,458
you look like a carp. And even
if you did look like a carp,

58
00:04:46,541 --> 00:04:48,666
you'd be the most beautiful
carp of them all!

59
00:04:48,750 --> 00:04:50,875
So I am a carp!

60
00:04:50,958 --> 00:04:53,291
Uh, no, that's
not what I meant.

61
00:04:53,375 --> 00:04:54,916
Tamaki, you're an idiot!

62
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,375
No wait! Mermaid Princess!

63
00:04:56,458 --> 00:04:58,250
Man, what a crybaby.

64
00:05:01,958 --> 00:05:03,333
So how's it going, boss?!

65
00:05:03,416 --> 00:05:06,500
That's an adorable little
apprentice you've got there.

66
00:05:06,583 --> 00:05:10,166
Hikaru, do you wish you had
a little brother like Shiro?

67
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:12,916
Don't be silly. I could search
the globe and I'd never find

68
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,166
