72
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:21,916
They're homos!
And they're brothers!

73
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,333
That makes this totally
"insectuous"!

74
00:05:24,416 --> 00:05:26,750
I think what you meant to say
was incestuous.

75
00:05:27,875 --> 00:05:29,125
Hey Shiro-chan!

76
00:05:29,208 --> 00:05:30,750
You wanna have
a piece of cake with me?

77
00:05:30,833 --> 00:05:34,291
We've got three kinds:
chocolate, strawberry and lime.

78
00:05:34,375 --> 00:05:36,583
Hey, back off! What grade
are you in, anyway?!

79
00:05:36,666 --> 00:05:39,416
Why are you wearing
a high school uniform?

80
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:41,250
Something wrong, Mitsukuni?

81
00:05:44,458 --> 00:05:46,333
That's not fair! A little kid
like you isn't supposed

82
00:05:46,416 --> 00:05:48,833
to have a cool,
older friend like him!

83
00:05:55,416 --> 00:05:57,291
Are you alright?

84
00:05:57,375 --> 00:05:59,125
I know. It's kinda hard
to get used to all

85
00:05:59,208 --> 00:06:01,666
the weirdos around here. It took
me a while to get adjusted

86
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:03,750
to all the craziness,
so don't freak out.

87
00:06:03,833 --> 00:06:05,458
I'm sure you'll get used to it.

88
00:06:06,416 --> 00:06:09,041
This one kinda acts
like a girl.

89
00:06:09,125 --> 00:06:09,750
Something wrong?

90
00:06:09,833 --> 00:06:11,333
