91
00:06:12,583 --> 00:06:13,875
Oh, no.

92
00:06:13,958 --> 00:06:16,458
Okay, that's enough.
I think Shiro should take care

93
00:06:16,541 --> 00:06:17,750
of the tea for us,
don't you?

94
00:06:17,833 --> 00:06:20,166
Wow, Haruhi, you're
looking extra manly today!

95
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:21,666
Now do what the boss says
and let Shiro take care

96
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:23,708
of that tea set,
it's part of his training.

97
00:06:23,791 --> 00:06:25,875
You're too macho
for tea sets.

98
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,375
This kid is smarter
than I thought.

99
00:06:36,458 --> 00:06:38,791
He may be a kid
but he's got quite an eye.

100
00:06:39,875 --> 00:06:41,833
Now be careful with it.
It's pretty heavy.

101
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:46,000
It's not my fault
I dropped it.

102
00:06:46,083 --> 00:06:47,791
It's your fault 'cause
you're the one who made me

103
00:06:47,875 --> 00:06:49,916
take it in the first place.

104
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,166
Say what?

105
00:06:51,250 --> 00:06:52,916
Haruhi, that's
another 100,000 yen.

106
00:06:53,708 --> 00:06:55,166
Hey! You should
make the cross-dresser do

107
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:57,333
