I'm not here to carry
tea sets- I'm here to learn

109
00:06:59,041 --> 00:07:00,666
how to make women happy!

110
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,166
You won't get anywhere
with that attitude.

111
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:06,750
And I am not going to let you
disrespect Haruhi. So!

112
00:07:08,125 --> 00:07:09,625
Put this brat in isolation!

113
00:07:09,708 --> 00:07:10,875
You got it, boss!

114
00:07:13,458 --> 00:07:14,583
What's going on here?!

115
00:07:14,666 --> 00:07:17,041
Why'd you put me in
a cage all of a sudden?!

116
00:07:17,125 --> 00:07:18,250
Yeah, where'd it come from?

117
00:07:18,333 --> 00:07:20,833
This is supposed to be
a music room, right?

118
00:07:20,916 --> 00:07:22,625
This is no way to treat
your loyal apprentice!

119
00:07:22,708 --> 00:07:24,708
Now let me out of this cage!

120
00:07:24,791 --> 00:07:26,375
Not until you've learned
your lesson. I made you

121
00:07:26,458 --> 00:07:28,166
my apprentice because I thought
you were serious about

122
00:07:28,250 --> 00:07:32,333
becoming a host but
I guess I was wrong.

123
00:07:32,416 --> 00:07:35,250
I am serious.
Totally serious.

124
00:07:38,333 --> 00:07:40,750
I want you to teach me
how to make a woman happy!

125
00:07:44,333 --> 00:07:50,000
I'm gonna run out of time.
Please, won't you teach me?

126
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:52,166
You're a host because
you like girls.

127
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:55,291
You like bringing a smile
to a girl's face- that's why

128
00:07:55,375 --> 00:07:57,166
you do it, right?

129
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:00,666
Please, won't you teach me
how to be like you?

130
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:03,666
You're a genius at it!
You're the king!

131
00:08:07,875 --> 00:08:10,208
Well, you may be a brat,
but I admire your desire

132
00:08:10,291 --> 00:08:12,750
to become a host,
so I'll teach you.

133
00:08:15,250 --> 00:08:17,875
You know, Shiro,
you and I are so much alike.

134
00:08:17,958 --> 00:08:19,458
You poor kid.

135
00:08:19,541 --> 00:08:20,416
Then you'll help me
become the kind of host

136
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:22,833
that can make any woman happy?!

137
00:08:22,916 --> 00:08:24,541
Of course, making women
happy is the sole purpose

138
00:08:24,625 --> 00:08:29,083
of being a host. If this is
what you really want Shiro,

139
00:08:29,166 --> 00:08:31,416
then you have to figure out
how to use the material

140
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:33,541
you already have.

141
00:08:33,625 --> 00:08:34,583
What does that mean?

142
00:08:34,666 --> 00:08:37,375
You see, here at
the Ouran Host Club.

143
00:08:37,458 --> 00:08:39,916
Our policy is to use our
individual personality traits

144
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,833
to meet the needs
of our guests. For example,

145
00:08:42,916 --> 00:08:45,333
there's Tamaki, who is
the princely type.

146
00:08:47,291 --> 00:08:49,625
There's the strong,
silent type.

147
00:08:49,708 --> 00:08:52,833
The boy Lolita type.

148
00:08:52,916 --> 00:08:55,416
The little devil type.

149
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,833
And the cool type.

150
00:08:56,916 --> 00:09:00,666
It's all about variety.
And now our group is complete

151
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:03,166
with the addition
of Haruhi, the natural.

152
00:09:05,583 --> 00:09:07,541
The natural?

153
00:09:07,625 --> 00:09:08,875
It would seem that right now
we have a perfect blend

154
00:09:08,958 --> 00:09:10,583
of characteristics,
so it's going to be

155
00:09:10,666 --> 00:09:12,833
difficult to find
a new type for Shiro.

156
00:09:14,541 --> 00:09:18,291
If you go by his age, he
should be the boy Lolita type.

157
00:09:18,375 --> 00:09:19,083
But Honey-senpai's
already got that covered.

158
00:09:19,166 --> 00:09:22,166
Is he gonna replace me?

159
00:09:22,250 --> 00:09:23,958
Oh come on! Is that
all you've got?

160
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:31,416
What's up with this place? It's
supposed to be a music room.

161
00:09:32,625 --> 00:09:35,083
Sorry to interrupt gentlemen,
but what's with the lackluster

162
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:38,291
character analysis? I must
say, I'm quite disappointed.

163
00:09:38,375 --> 00:09:40,875
I thought I taught you better.

164
00:09:40,958 --> 00:09:43,375
Alright then, Miss Manager.
How would you work Shiro

165
00:09:43,458 --> 00:09:45,500
into our collection of
characters? He can't be

166
00:09:45,583 --> 00:09:48,875
the boy Lolita because Honey's
already got that covered.

167
00:09:48,958 --> 00:09:51,000
You just don't
get it, do you?

168
00:09:51,083 --> 00:09:52,583
Now listen up! There are
plenty of girls out there

169
00:09:52,666 --> 00:09:55,583
who have a thing for younger
boys or boys with baby faces.

170
00:09:55,666 --> 00:09:57,875
These girls would be
considered shota fans.

171
00:09:57,958 --> 00:10:00,000
Now, shota can be
a fairly broad category

172
00:10:00,083 --> 00:10:01,875
so it's important to know
that the genre can be

173
00:10:01,958 --> 00:10:04,875
broken down into many different
smaller sub-categories.

174
00:10:04,958 --> 00:10:07,333
For example, shota fans with
an interest in Lolita boys

175
00:10:07,416 --> 00:10:09,708
would favor a boy like
Haninozuka-senpai.

176
00:10:09,791 --> 00:10:12,583
But this little boy is
different. If I had to pick

177
00:10:12,666 --> 00:10:15,125
a character for him.

178
00:10:15,208 --> 00:10:17,625
Yes! He'd be the naughty-boy
type, without a doubt!

179
00:10:19,208 --> 00:10:20,250
The naughty type?

180
00:10:25,791 --> 00:10:26,583
Now to play up
the naughty type,

181
00:10:26,666 --> 00:10:29,375
you have to wear shorts, okay!

182
00:10:31,458 --> 00:10:32,625
You've gotta have
bumps and bruises!

183
00:10:32,708 --> 00:10:34,666
Give him a couple of scars!

184
00:10:36,583 --> 00:10:39,208
Run like a spoiled child!
Make it reckless!

185
00:10:40,791 --> 00:10:42,666
Now I want you to trip
and make it big!

186
00:10:46,500 --> 00:10:48,541
"Are you okay, little boy?"

187
00:10:48,625 --> 00:10:51,291
Now give them
your catch phrase!

188
00:10:51,375 --> 00:10:53,583
No big deal,
it was nothin'.

189
00:10:53,666 --> 00:10:58,541
That was perfect!
Absolutely perfect, Shiro!

190
00:10:58,625 --> 00:11:00,083
That was outstanding.

191
00:11:00,166 --> 00:11:03,500
I never knew you were such
a great coach, Renge.

192
00:11:03,583 --> 00:11:07,333
They're idiots!
They're all a bunch of idiots!

193
00:11:07,416 --> 00:11:08,833
I've had enough of you people!

194
00:11:10,583 --> 00:11:12,166
This is so stupid- none
of this is ever gonna help me

195
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:13,833
make her happy!

196
00:11:13,916 --> 00:11:15,750
Who's her?

197
00:11:15,833 --> 00:11:17,041
Wait Shiro! We haven't
taught you how

198
00:11:17,125 --> 00:11:19,208
to apply the techniques
you've learned yet!

199
00:11:20,833 --> 00:11:23,375
I swear, younger boys
are good for nothing.

200
00:11:23,458 --> 00:11:27,250
I went to all that trouble
to coach him, and he quits.

201
00:11:27,333 --> 00:11:28,708
I can't believe
he ditched us because

202
00:11:28,791 --> 00:11:31,333
he didn't like the lesson.
What a selfish little brat.

203
00:11:31,416 --> 00:11:33,083
There aren't many people who'd
enjoy that kinda lesson.

204
00:11:33,166 --> 00:11:35,875
But never mind that, were you
listening to what he said?

205
00:11:37,583 --> 00:11:40,958
I'm gonna run out of time.
Please, won't you teach me?

206
00:11:42,791 --> 00:11:44,125
He said he was "gonna run out
of time"- what do you think

207
00:11:44,208 --> 00:11:48,583
that means? I think,
maybe, it's a girl.

208
00:12:01,083 --> 00:12:04,416
How did we let them
talk us into this?

209
