212
00:12:11,666 --> 00:12:13,750
Yeah, you do. I understand
why they wanted you

213
00:12:13,833 --> 00:12:15,500
to wear an elementary
school uniform.

214
00:12:15,583 --> 00:12:17,708
I mean, we are sneaking
into an elementary school

215
00:12:17,791 --> 00:12:21,041
and you totally fit in,
senpai. What I don't understand

216
00:12:21,125 --> 00:12:24,458
is why they made me dress up
in this middle school uniform.

217
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,375
Alright men, it's time
to initiate our mission.

218
00:12:28,458 --> 00:12:29,375
What do you mean?

219
00:12:29,458 --> 00:12:30,750
What mission?

220
00:12:30,833 --> 00:12:32,458
I've assessed the situation.
We'll infiltrate

221
00:12:32,541 --> 00:12:36,791
the elementary school.
You two are going in!

222
00:12:36,875 --> 00:12:38,250
But where are we going?

223
00:12:38,333 --> 00:12:39,500
Why did we even bother
with disguises?

224
00:12:39,583 --> 00:12:41,916
We stick out like a sore thumb!

225
00:12:44,541 --> 00:12:47,666
Oh, there's a reason,
a damn good reason.

226
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:49,041
This way, Haru-chan!

227
00:12:49,125 --> 00:12:51,041
Isn't she the cutest?

228
00:12:51,125 --> 00:12:55,291
Look at her in that miniskirt.
Haruhi looks like a little doll.

229
00:12:55,375 --> 00:12:57,750
So basically, you just wanted to
see her dressed up like that.

230
00:13:00,583 --> 00:13:02,041
This is it.
Shiro-chan's classroom.

231
00:13:02,125 --> 00:13:05,333
When I was in elementary school
this was my classroom, too!

232
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:12,583
